display_long_description:
Factory Outbreak: Zombie Eradication plunges you into a terrifying industrial landscape where survival is your only option. When a mysterious infection spreads through the factory, normal workers transform into ruthless zombies, turning the assembly line into a battleground. Your mission is to navigate this chaos, fend off the undead, and escape before it’s too late!

Key Features
Immersive Industrial Environment
Explore a detailed factory setting filled with ominous machinery, dark corners, and abandoned workspaces. The atmosphere is rich with tension, creating an engaging backdrop for your fight for survival.
Intense Zombie Combat
Face waves of relentless zombies that were once your coworkers. Use an array of weapons—from makeshift tools to powerful firearms—to eliminate the infected. 
Survival Mechanics
Collect resources, craft items, and manage your inventory wisely. Every decision counts as you scavenge for weapons and supplies while trying to stay one step ahead of the undead.
Challenging Gameplay
Navigate through various levels of the factory, each presenting unique challenges and enemy types. Use stealth, speed, and cunning to outsmart the zombies and find your way to safety.
Storyline
After a lab accident leads to a catastrophic outbreak, the factory is quarantined. As one of the few survivors, you must unravel the mystery behind the infection while fighting for your life. Each level reveals more about the outbreak and the chilling fate of your coworkers.
